Bike Riding Analysis – Power BI Project
🔹 Project Overview

This project analyzes bike riding data to understand rider behavior, trip patterns, fuel efficiency, and safety risks.

Using Python, SQL, and Power BI, the system evaluates:

Ride distance, duration, and speed
Fuel consumption
Rider habits and patterns
Safety indicators

👉 Final output: Interactive dashboard for performance monitoring & safety improvement

