🔹 Sample Python Logic (Simple Example)
# Calculate speed
df['speed'] = df['distance'] / df['time']

# Risk category
df['risk'] = df['speed'].apply(
    lambda x: 'High' if x > 80 else 'Medium' if x > 50 else 'Low'
)
🔹 SQL Example (Interview Ready)
-- Overspeed Trips
SELECT trip_id, speed
FROM rides
WHERE speed > 80;
